/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝咁多位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地要繼續撐落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地唔係得自己一個㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左美國之外 我地都要同埋唔同國家講聲多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好辜負人地既心血<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:01:18.000Z","msg":"嘩年紀好大<br />\n法國老人都高質"},{"pid":"7b6a2b4524c0864c858acebf0fae616139d7192d","tid":1570342,"uid":146458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:01:19.000Z","msg":"遍地開花 銅記見"},{"pid":"a2212473b2d34e0db304ad52a0e8ac2a053a6188","tid":1570342,"uid":146458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"遍地開花 銅記見"},{"pid":"14f1d3e5c5cca9c0767b30454e8c4d562e779c36","tid":1570342,"uid":120264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:01:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75e1012cd033ae86d9b9762761d5e31b0633ae6d","tid":1570342,"uid":66178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:02:19.000Z","msg":"可唔可以請佢地929都搞多次?"}]}